  # Create Form
  
  Creates a new empty form container.
  
  * **URL:** `/forms`
  * **Method:** `POST`
  * **Auth Required:** Yes
  
  ### Request Body
  
  | Field | Type | Required | Description |
  | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
  | `title` | `string` | Yes | The display title of the form. |
  | `description` | `string` | No | A short description or instructions for the form. |
  
  **Sample Input:**
  
  ```json
  {
    "title": "Hackathon Registration",
    "description": "Please fill out your team details."
  }
  
  Responses
  âœ… 200 OK: Created
  
  Returns the newly created form object.
  JSON
  
  {
    "success": true,
    "message": "Form created successfully",
